
# Simple To-Do List App

A minimalist web-based To-Do List application built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.

## Features

- **Add tasks** to your list.
- **Check off completed tasks**.
- **Delete tasks** you no longer need.

## Demo

Open `index.html` in your browser to start using the app.

## Technologies Used

- **HTML**
- **CSS**
- **JavaScript**

## Project Structure

```
├── index.html
├── style.css
└── script.js
```

## About

This app is designed for simplicity and ease of use. There is no setup required—just open the HTML file and start organizing your tasks!

